  <brief_title>To Investigate the Safety and Tolerability of Repeated Subcutaneous Injections of CAD106 in Alzheimer's Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label Extension to a 52-week, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group Study in Patients With Alzheimer's Disease to Investigate the Safety and Tolerability of Repeated Subcutaneous Injections of CAD106.</official_title>
